Minutes:  Clerk/T. Lehman.  ADA James Kraus appeared for the State.  Deft appeared in person w/Atty Diane Caspari.  Case is resolved.  State stipulates to a plea of not guilty by reason of mental disease or defect to count 1.  Deft's previous plea of not guilty & not guilty by mental disease or defect is changed to a plea of not guilty by mental disease or defect.  Remaining counts are dismissed on State's motion. Court orders the Dept of Health Services to complete a pre-dispositional report.  Sentencing set for 4/24/17 @ 11:15am.  Report to be provided to the court by 4/20/17.
